/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81b0bbd1ebc4c606c58c8707044438c40e453d7","tid":1493884,"uid":237096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"好驚，佢會唔會比人虐待 同菊花不保架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e5801389bae002ecc83c9e6ca500c8e480b088","tid":1493884,"uid":133715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:15:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>未有收到拘留通知書<br />\n</strong><br />\n聲明指出：「家人於8月9日曾向警方及入境處求助，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">僅被告知可自行回內地報案</span></strong>。入境處與駐粵辦聯繫後，於8月10日<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">口頭告知</span></span>家人Simon被<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行政拘留</span></span>，但稱<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無法得悉拘留原因、場所和期限</span>。家人至今未有收到內地有關部門的行政拘留通知書；根據相關法例，該通知書理應於Simon被扣押24小時內發出。家人亦從未收過任何文件確認Simon是被當局正式拘留。」<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱：「經律師查證，該案為深圳市公安局負責，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">但至今仍未能查知Simon被關押於何處，亦未能會見律師</span></span>。深圳市拘留所、寶安區拘留所、南山區拘留所<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">都沒有Simon的影子</span></span></strong>。廣洲及深圳的兩家派出所，以及廣州鐵路公安局<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">均稱不知道Simon 的下落</span></span></strong>。」家人對此感到非常無助，「很擔心Simon的安危，很希望Simon能早日回港。」"},{"pid":"a045bfa8aa9bbd65462f9264096e4294470df057","tid":1493884,"uid":133715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81b0bbd1ebc4c606c58c8707044438c40e453d7","tid":1493884,"uid":237096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"好驚，佢會唔會比人虐待 同菊花不保架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能已經比人溶左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197c8e80b001287cf44981d157b851a868814821","tid":1493884,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"用weixin 所以比人捉"},{"pid":"2ce2dc15427384ea649bbb2a4474232aad18f968","tid":1493884,"uid":284304,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"197c8e80b001287cf44981d157b851a868814821","tid":1493884,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"用weixin 所以比人捉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"sorry係wechat"},{"pid":"60bbf15e68566b3f300eb7190988a2c39da0163f","tid":1493884,"uid":133715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197c8e80b001287cf44981d157b851a868814821","tid":1493884,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"用weixin 所以比人捉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"用咩都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過個境就被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似無咩人提呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk